v^3+a_2v^2+a_1v+a_0=0
\left|v\right|<4
\left|v^3\right|\leq3(\left|v\right|^2+\left|v\right|+1)\implies\left|v^3\right|-1\leq3(\left|v\right|^2+\left|v\right|+1)-1\implies\dots\implies\left|v\right|-1<3\\ \implies\left|v\right|<4
